Yiwen wergaz iruḥ ad yejbu ɣef weltma-s, imi yewweḍ yufa-tt ulac-itt deg wexxam, netta ur yuẓam ara, yufa aqbuc n yiɣi ɣef udekkan yekker yerra-t ɣef yimi-s, yettu ur yesfiḍ ara claɣem-is, ur tɛeṭṭel ara attah tekcem-d weltma-s, imi tsellem fell-as testeqsa-t:
-Amek i tettiliḍ ?
Yerra-yas-d:
-aql-ikem tettwaliḍ anebdu rnu-yas remḍan.
Dɣa tenna-yas:
-“mi ara nsel i yimi numen, mi nessakked ɣer claɣem newhem”
